---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2025-01-01';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy" description="Learn how Voxeia uses cookies and similar technologies.">
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 overflow-hidden gradient-mesh">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black font-display text-text">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose-dark space-y-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            This Cookie Policy explains how Voxeia uses cookies and similar tracking technologies when you visit our
            website and use our platform.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help websites remember
            your preferences and improve your browsing experience. We also use similar technologies such as pixels,
            local storage, and session storage.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 mt-4">
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Essential Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Required for the platform to function. These handle authentication, security, and core functionality.
                Cannot be disabled.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-2">Duration: Session to 1 year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Analytics Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Help us understand how visitors interact with our website. We use these to improve performance and user
                experience. Data is anonymized and aggregated.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-2">Duration: Up to 2 years</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Functional Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Remember your preferences such as language, region, and display settings to provide a personalized
                experience.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-2">Duration: Up to 1 year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Marketing Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Used to deliver relevant advertisements and measure the effectiveness of our marketing campaigns. These
                may be set by third-party advertising partners.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-2">Duration: Up to 2 years</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Some cookies are placed by third-party services that appear on our pages:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li><strong class="text-text">Google Analytics:</strong> Website usage analytics</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Intercom:</strong> Customer support chat</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Stripe:</strong> Payment processing</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">LinkedIn Insight Tag:</strong> Marketing analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">You can control cookies through:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-text">Browser Settings:</strong> Most browsers allow you to block or delete cookies through
              their settings menu
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-text">Our Cookie Banner:</strong> Use the cookie preferences banner when you first visit
              our site to opt in or out of non-essential cookies
            </li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Do Not Track:</strong> We respect browser Do Not Track (DNT) signals</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Note: Disabling essential cookies may prevent certain features from functioning correctly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">5. Updates to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Cookie Policy periodically. Check this page for the latest information about our cookie
            practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">6. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Questions about our use of cookies? Contact us:</p>
          <div class="mt-4 p-6 bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl">
            <p class="text-text font-semibold">Voxeia Privacy Team</p>
            <p class="text-text-muted mt-1">
              Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@voxeia.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">privacy@voxeia.com</a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-text-muted mt-1">100% Remote Company</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
